{"tid":905314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【APEC】彭斯：中國改變前　貿易戰沒有終止的一天","createTime":"2018-11-17T04:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T23:58:27.000Z","uid":147314,"like":125,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2206f8cf61d6924a31d629cca0cc3c1e59290a","tid":905314,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"美副總統：中國改變前 美關稅不會鬆手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20181116/446217538551.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20181116%2F446217538551.jpg&h=e71abae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（中央社巴紐首都莫士比港17日綜合外電報導）美國副總統彭斯（Mike Pence）今天表示，在中國修正自身貿易政策前，美國不會停止對付中國的相關貿易手段。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯在巴布亞紐幾內亞的亞太經合會（APEC）峰會上指出，在中國調整政策前，美國不會移除對中國加徵的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯說：「我們已果斷採取行動處理與中國間的失衡，我們已對2500億美元的中國貨品加徵關稅，且還可以再加倍。美國不會改變作法，直到中國改變自身的行為。」<br />\n<br />\n（譯者：陳亦偉/核稿：蔡佳敏）1071117<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201811170032.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201811170032.aspx&d=s3MI7VAOkm5bhBhmo8PddP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1ea2f811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201811170032.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"f84ed37a1031e052c8dcbac82a01fb3ddaf71304","tid":905314,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227075253c802e068987a113775f5eb87d65ce78","tid":905314,"uid":147314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:36:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Pence vows no end to tariffs until China bows</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">NOVEMBER 17, 2018 / 10:46 AM / UPDATED 8 MINUTES AGO</span><br />\n<br />\nPORT MORESBY (Reuters) - The United States will not back down from its trade dispute with China, and might even double its tariffs, unless Beijing bows to U.S. demands, Vice President Mike Pence said on Saturday.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s2.reutersmedia.net/resources/r/?m=02&amp;d=20181117&amp;t=2&amp;i=1326143665&amp;r=LYNXNPEEAG04C&amp;w=1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.reutersmedia.net%2Fresources%2Fr%2F%3Fm%3D02%26d%3D20181117%26t%3D2%26i%3D1326143665%26r%3DLYNXNPEEAG04C%26w%3D1280&h=c0284d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">U.S. Vice President Mike Pence speaks during the APEC CEO Summit 2018 at Port Moresby, Papua New Guinea, 17 November 2018. Fazry Ismail/Pool via REUTERS</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-apec-summit-usa/pence-vows-no-end-to-tariffs-until-china-bows-idUSKCN1NM04K\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-apec-summit-usa%2Fpence-vows-no-end-to-tariffs-until-china-bows-idUSKCN1NM04K&d=s3MI7VAOkm5bhBhmo8PddP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=b3d36993\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-apec-summit-usa%2Fpence-vows-no-end-to-tariffs-until-china-bows-idUSKCN1NM04K&h=0cdb23a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-apec-summit-usa/pence-vows-no-end-to-tariffs-until-china-bows-idUSKCN1NM04K</a>"},{"pid":"49a7b8d0c3d906aa281d7481e487c3f6cd262631","tid":905314,"uid":147314,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:38:21.000Z","msg":"In a bluntly worded speech at an Asia Pacific Economic Co-operation (APEC) summit in Papua New Guinea, Pence threw down the gauntlet to China on trade and security in the region.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We have taken decisive action to address our imbalance with China,&rdquo; Pence declared. <span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;We put tariffs on $250 billion in Chinese goods, and we could more than double that number.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The United States, though, will not change course until China changes its ways.&rdquo;</span>"},{"pid":"5848e2a3f21b7bb73b7556a43ae7bc845d1bc65d","tid":905314,"uid":207087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"最後贏家是誰"},{"pid":"296f4dc4bfad50f3d30ce052ccb28317da304adb","tid":905314,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:42:20.000Z","msg":"The stark warning will likely be unwelcome news to financial markets which had hoped for a thaw in the Sino-U.S. dispute and perhaps even some sort of deal at a G20 meeting later this month in Argentina.<br />\n<br />\nU.S. President Donald Trump, who is not attending the APEC meeting, is due to meet Chinese President Xi Jinping in Argentina.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Pence&rsquo;s warning on Saturday contrasted with remarks made by Trump on Friday</span>, when he said he may not impose more tariffs after China sent the United States a list of measures it was willing to take to resolve trade tensions."},{"pid":"a6ad4f2f5d43b7faef2becc66c61c78894b6f0af","tid":905314,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:44:50.000Z","msg":"Trump has imposed tariffs on $250 billion worth of Chinese imports to force concessions on a list of demands that would change the terms of trade between the two countries. China has responded with import tariffs on U.S. goods.<br />\n<br />\nWashington is demanding Beijing improve market access and intellectual property protections for U.S. companies, cut industrial subsidies and slash a $375 billion trade gap.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">There was no hint of compromise from Pence.</span>"},{"pid":"60ae978d159067c43ef9f7e2ec7e197357855171","tid":905314,"uid":4285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"又撚"},{"pid":"8c08475cf2ca1f8926655e9d8b6e8638cf1a0561","tid":905314,"uid":6604,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"Mike Pence 2024 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329f1d00f4b7a5337ffe66ed5e9ffaedbc214a05","tid":905314,"uid":23635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5848e2a3f21b7bb73b7556a43ae7bc845d1bc65d","tid":905314,"uid":207087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:39:23.000Z","msg":"最後贏家是誰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"肯定唔係強国"},{"pid":"cf4e2459806d97de3d41f05275b9a26adce1f941","tid":905314,"uid":56147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"呢個彭斯先係真大中華膠"},{"pid":"ee37fa0f56c49e9dfd4c520af1a7dc255d48e79d","tid":905314,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"8c08475cf2ca1f8926655e9d8b6e8638cf1a0561","tid":905314,"uid":6604,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"Mike Pence 2024 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:47:08.000Z","msg":"2020啦，trump成日同鷹派打對台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdbfbffb6f59c3729a5b6fa1ff733c7e0dadd5e","tid":905314,"uid":76470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:47:45.000Z","msg":"好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073522e634db6ef8839e086b1bab68a19cdef629","tid":905314,"uid":147314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;China has taken advantage of the United States for many years. <span style=\"color: red;\">Those days are over</span>,&rdquo; he told delegates gathered on a cruise liner docked in Port Moresby&rsquo;s Fairfax Harbour.<br />\n<br />\nHe also took aim at China&rsquo;s territorial ambitions in the Pacific and, particularly, <span style=\"color: red;\">Xi&rsquo;s Belt and Road Initiative</span> to expand land and sea links between Asia, Africa and Europe with billions of dollars in infrastructure investment.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">We don&rsquo;t offer constricting belts or a one-way road</span>,&rdquo; said Pence."},{"pid":"805779d80755c798602d6a9dba1b3a7e24fecc00","tid":905314,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":35,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:48:34.000Z","msg":"美國寧願滅忙都唔放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係咁要面"},{"pid":"ac4a4c44b4009e3ca7ccc9e4e66db8e2321018d5","tid":905314,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"發唔發覺哩排侵既內閣個個講野都唔一樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然內容唔算矛盾，但個tone好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80923a5c5d542e246fe29aabfbe5debd721694ff","tid":905314,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdd7d8e8039bd14acec9a73aed416ccda8ac234","tid":905314,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf4e2459806d97de3d41f05275b9a26adce1f941","tid":905314,"uid":56147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"呢個彭斯先係真大中華膠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:49:21.000Z","msg":"建設民主中國"},{"pid":"44ea815a14aefa5fad5ea07824c9696053d3a460","tid":905314,"uid":31946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:49:29.000Z","msg":"打佢 打佢老母 打佢 打佢老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass